    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P58"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Adevrul_asupra_trecutului_i_prezentului_Basarabiei#cite_ref-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Revista coala Basarabiei, 1920; Reviste Istoric, IV, p. 52-53. Am dat o form modernizat, mai uor de neles, acestei plngeri.</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P58"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Adevrul_asupra_trecutului_i_prezentului_Basarabiei#cite_ref-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aceste ultime dou paragrafe au fost adugate de N. Iorga la ediia n limba romn a Adevrului ... (vezi infra), dup ocuparea Basarabiei i Bucovinei de Nord n urma notelor ultimative ale lui V. M. Molotov din 26-27 iunie 1940. Istoricul a procedat ntocmai i n cazul ediiei n limba rus (vezi Pravda o prolom i nastoiacem Bessarabii, p. 55).</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
