     <text:p text:style-name="P66"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Romnia_mam_a_unitii_naionale/Romanai#cite_ref-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aici am prea puin de schimbat. Universul s-a prefcut ns cu vremea ntr-o cetire serioas i profitabil (1916).</text:span></text:p>
