     <text:p text:style-name="P67"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Romnia_mam_a_unitii_naionale/Argeul#cite_ref-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Astzi, mulmit arhitectului Cerchez, strlucita biseric e deplin salvat, spre admiraia celor de acas i a strinilor. i d. Virgil Drghiceanu a scos la iveal nsui trupul lui Basarab ctitorul (1939).</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
