     <text:p text:style-name="P68"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Romnia_mam_a_unitii_naionale/Argeul#cite_ref-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Astzi rmiile lor sunt acolo, ale amndurora, mbriate recunosctor de bunul pmnt al rii care e mai mult frmntat cu oasele strbunilor notri (1916). i alturi dorm regele Ferdinand i acea minune de frumuse i inteligen, regina Maria (1939).</text:span></text:p>
