     <text:p text:style-name="P68"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Romnia_mam_a_unitii_naionale/Argeul#cite_ref-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">O clip, tristea unei regine singuratece s-a odihnit aici, apoi pustiul a revenit, poate pentru totdeauna (1916).</text:span></text:p>
